---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/digipom.css';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Digipom">
	<section class="px-4 py-3 lg:px-0 mb-14 lg:max-w-[1110px] lg:mx-auto md:flex items-center justify-center">
		<div class="flex flex-col w-[398px] sm:w-full md:items-center md:w-[732px]">
			<div class="font-bold md:text-twentytwo text-dpgreen mb-3">Who are we?</div>
			<div class="font-bold text-forty tracking-tight leading-normal mb-4">
				Welcome to <span class="text-dpgreen">Digipom</span>
			</div>
			<p class="text-dpdarkblue text-opacity-60 text-lg md:text-twentytwo md:text-center">
				We’re an independent development studio that was started in March 2012, and we’ve been creating fun, intuitive, and easy-to-use apps for mobile ever since.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
	
	<section class="px-4 py-3 lg:px-0 mb-32 lg:max-w-[1110px] lg:mx-auto md:flex">
		<div class="flex flex-col">
			<div class="font-bold md:text-twentytwo text-dpgreen mb-3">Our motto and values</div>
			<div class="md:max-w-[1062px] font-bold text-twentytwo md:text-thirtyfour tracking-tight leading-normal mb-4">
				We believe that a pleasant user experience is first and foremost.
			</div>
			<p class="text-dpdarkblue text-opacity-60 md:text-twentytwo">
				An app doesn’t have to have fancy graphics, but it should be easy to understand and easy to use. Ads are acceptable, but they should never be intrusive. Our goal is to treat our users with respect, and deliver value that exceeds their expectations.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
